&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with inventory planning concepts and theory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Top-notch analytical, financial modeling and problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of product and trend as it relates to the business&lt;/li&gt;
